# DESCRIPTION
# Determine the domain and range of f(x) = sqrt(x^2 - B)
#
# ENDDESCRIPTION
## DBsubject(Algebra)
## DBchapter(Functions)
## DBsection(Domain and range)
## Institution(John Wiley & Sons)
## MLT(AlgDom3)
## Level(2)
## MO(1)
